Talloc2 is lightweight implementation of talloc api. License - LGPL v3.
1. Minimal sizeof talloc_chunk is 32 bytes (amd64).
2. Save memory without performance penalties.
2. Configurable extensions.
3. CMake build system. Project is ready to be added as git submodule to existing CMake project.


Implemented & covered by tests
core:
void *  talloc         ( const void * ctx, size_t length );
void *  talloc_zero    ( const void * ctx, size_t length );
void *  talloc_realloc ( const void * ctx, size_t length );
uint8_t talloc_free    ( void * ctx );

helpers:
void *  talloc_new     ( const void * ctx );
char *  talloc_strdup  ( const void * ctx, const char * str );
char *  talloc_strndup ( const void * ctx, const char * str, size_t length );

extensions:
uint8_t talloc_set_destructor ( const void * ctx, uint8_t ( * destructor ) ( void * parent_data ) );
uint8_t talloc_get_length ( const void * ctx, size_t * result );
void *  talloc_mode       ( const void * ctx, size_t length, uint8_t mode );
void *  talloc_zero_mode  ( const void * ctx, size_t length, uint8_t mode );

modes:
TALLOC_MODE_LENGTH